WEBVTT

00:01:58.251 --> 00:02:00.606
(Vicheko)

00:02:00.630 --> 00:02:03.599
Nimeangalia maksi ya wanafunzi wa udaktari

00:02:03.623 --> 00:02:05.598
na hata mapato ya watu wa mauzo

00:02:05.622 --> 00:02:07.068
(Vicheko)

00:02:07.092 --> 00:02:08.744
Cha kushtua, ni

00:02:08.768 --> 00:02:12.437
watoaji wanafanya vibaya kuliko wote, katika kila fani.

00:02:12.749 --> 00:02:14.793
Wahandisi wanaofanya vibaya kazini

00:02:14.817 --> 00:02:17.323
ndio wanaotoa fadhila kuliko wanapokea.

00:02:17.347 --> 00:02:19.483
Wako makini kufanya kazi za watu wengine,

00:02:19.507 --> 00:02:23.057
hata hawana muda au nguvu ya 
kufanya kazi zao.

00:02:23.081 --> 00:02:25.886
Katika udaktari, maksi za chini ni za

00:02:25.910 --> 00:02:28.017
wanafunzi wanaokubaliana na kauli kama,

00:02:28.041 --> 00:02:30.249
"Ninapenda kuwasaidia wengine,"